OL,3,CShopkeeper shames shoplifters online
OL,4,Cin bid to reduce thefts
OL,6,FA shopkeeper in Kent has come up with
OL,7,Fan unusual way of stopping thefts from
OL,8,Fhis convenience store.
OL,10,FSuki Athwal posts CCTV footage of
OL,11,Falleged offenders on social media to
OL,12,Fpublicly shame them and he says a
OL,13,Fsurprising number of them come back
OL,14,Fand pay.
OL,16,FShop theft is running at record
OL,17,Flevels, and there are calls for
OL,18,Ftougher penalties for those who are
OL,19,Fcaught.
