OL,3,CShopkeeper shames shoplifters online
OL,4,Cin bid to reduce thefts
OL,6,FKent Police say they take retail crime
OL,7,Fvery seriously and are urging traders
OL,8,Fto report all offences to them rather
OL,9,Fthan posting information online.
OL,11,FMr Athwal's family have run the Shop
OL,12,FAround The Clock convenience store in
OL,13,FTenterden for the last 35 years but
OL,14,Frecently they've been dismayed by the
OL,15,Fnumber of customers who take goods off
OL,16,Fthe shelves and leave without paying.
OL,18,FHe is now posting CCTV footage of
OL,19,Falleged offenders on Facebook.
