OL,3,CShopkeeper shames shoplifters online
OL,4,Cin bid to reduce thefts
OL,6,FMr Athwal said: "We just started
OL,7,Fclipping up videos of when people have
OL,8,Fstolen from us and posted it online.
OL,10,F"I try to make it a bit of joke around
OL,11,Fit because I think we need to turn the
OL,12,Fnegative into a positive.
OL,14,F"We've found now that people are
OL,15,Fstarting to come back to us to pay or
OL,16,Ftheir family comes back as they've
OL,17,Fseen their relative online and they're
OL,18,Fa bit ashamed and disappointed in them
OL,19,F- and that's when I take the post down
OL,20,Fand that's starting to work for us."
