OL,3,CShopkeeper shames shoplifters online
OL,4,Cin bid to reduce thefts
OL,6,FSome shopkeepers say they've stopped
OL,7,Freporting thefts because nothing
OL,8,Fhappens but Kent Police say they take
OL,9,Fthe crime very seriously.
OL,11,F"We've got more officers out on the
OL,12,Fbeat, in town centers, in
OL,13,Fneighbourhoods. Every ward in Kent has
OL,14,Fa dedicated, named officer who can be
OL,15,Fcontacted via the Kent Police website.
