OL,3,CShopkeeper shames shoplifters online
OL,4,Cin bid to reduce thefts
OL,6,F"We engage regularly with local
OL,7,Fbusinesses and key partners and
OL,8,Fstakeholders to understand what their
OL,9,Fconcerns are, particularly around
OL,10,Fretail crime which is a real priority
OL,11,Fas a force and organisation so I think
OL,12,Fwe're doing a great deal to try and
OL,13,Fget out there, be visible, prevent
OL,14,Fcrime and when a crime is reported, do
OL,15,Four very best to investigate it
OL,16,Fthoroughly."
OL,18,FSuki Athwal says shop theft has become
OL,19,Fmore of a problem since the cost of
OL,20,Fliving crisis. But this is not a
OL,21,Fvictimless crime.
